high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to the table. Make a right to face the table.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Turn to the right and then left to walk around the table to the other side.
Set the tomato on the table.
Pick up the yellow knife from the table.
Use the knife to slice the tomato.
Set the knife on the table to the right of the sponge.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn around and go to the left. Then make another left at the oven.
Place the tomato slice on the skillet.
Pick up the skillet with the tomato slice.
Turn to the left and walk over to the table. Turn left again to face the table.
Place the skillet on the table with the tomato inside.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato and place in skillet.

high_descs: Turn left then head towards the table against the wall.
From the table pick up the tomato behind the green sponge.
Turn right then head towards the door, turn left then head towards the refrigerator, then left, head towards the table.
Place the tomato to the right of the green sponge.
Pick up the knife behind the spoon on the table
Cut the tomato into slices.
Place the knife behind the tomato on the table.
Pick up a tomato from the table.
Turn left, then head towards the stove.
Place the tomato into the frying pan on the stove.
Pick up the frying pan from the stove.
Turn left then head towards the table against the wall.
Place the frying pan to the left of the plant onto the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a frying pan with a tomato slice in it onto the table.
